# Helm Installation Instructions:

Add repository
`helm repo add jfrog https://charts.jfrog.io `

Install JFrog platform using helm chart
`helm install jfrog-platform --create-namespace -n jfrog-platform jfrog/jfrog-platform --set artifactory.mc.enabled=false --set distribution.enabled=false --set redis.enabled=false --set pipelines.enabled=false --set insight.enabled=false`

# Ubuntu Installation Instructions:
1. Download the installer
`wget -O jfrog-deb-installer.tar.gz "https://releases.jfrog.io/artifactory/jfrog-prox/org/artifactory/pro/deb/jfrog-platform-trial-prox/[RELEASE]/jfrog-platform-trial-prox-[RELEASE]-deb.tar.gz"`
2. Extract the installer
`tar -xvzf jfrog-deb-installer.tar.gz`
3. Extract the installer
`cd jfrog-platform-trial-pro*`
4. Run the installer
`sudo ./install.sh`
5. Start Artifactory
`sudo systemctl start artifactory.service`
6. Start Xray
`sudo systemctl start xray.service`
7. Open Browser
`http://localhost:8082/`
